                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Hehe, the charm/DC thing is normal.  Most enchanters don't charm.  Takes a bit of experience, gear, and AAs to support, plus they are risk averse.  So most non-raider types when they see an enchanter charm think DC, because that's all the enchanters they know bother with.
<br />

<br />
I recommend LDoN for getting experience with charm, by the way.  Provides a great way to ramp up, from charmed, to charmed with haste, to the full dual wielding, hasted, mage geared pet:)</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
