                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Suits are not charmable, Humans are.  Be aware that some of them will summon.  
<br />

<br />
If you are working the GY with your friends have them pull the suits from the right till they can pull a human out.  Tash, Snare then CoD Charm.
<br />

<br />
You now have a pet that will outdamage your entire party  <img src="images/smiles/icon_eek.gif" alt="icon_eek.gif" border="0" />.  Be warned, charm will break.  Make a hotkey to tell the group that the pet had broken and that it needs to be resnared.
<br />

<br />
Stay ready for charm breaks, keep your distance and never ever go AFK while you have the pet charmed.
<br />

<br />
Charming is a strategy that takes practice.  It'll be a learning experience for your group, but one that is worth it.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-size: 9px; line-height: normal"><span style="color: darkred">Iumarex Mistweaver
<br />
Coercer
<br />
Quellious</span></span></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
